Registered Nurse Gail Macrae:
"These Covid protocols... [were] causing these patients to go into organ failure.... People say their loved ones died of Covid. I'm sorry, but that's not the way it went down. People actually died in the hospital from the protocols."
This clip of Macrae (
@Gail13007674
), RN, BSN, NP describing how the Covid hospital protocols were killing patients is taken from an interview with Apollo the Original (
@apollotheorigin
) posted to YouTube on October 9, 2025.
